message: 1、升级生成'Magisk卡模块'的模板到最新的版本||2、适配Android 9和Android 10的息屏刷卡功能（支持大部分类原生Android系统，国内定制的系统没测试过）||3、修复还原操作导致小米MIUI和一加的nfc功能无法正常工作的bug||4、适配product分区
message_en: 1、Upgrade the template of 'Magisk Module' to the latest version.||2、Adapt Edxposed(Xposed) features(Enable NFC pooling while 'phone is locked and screen is off' for Android 9 and above) (support most native Android systems)||3、Fix the bug that the restore operation causes Xiaomi MIUI and OnePlus' nfc function to not work properly.||4、Adapt product partition.
